``tightness in his shoulder.'' No further information was 
available. 
</P>
<P>
	Derek Lowe replaced him.  
</P>
<P>
	Saberhagen, who missed most of the 1996 and '97 seasons  
following shoulder surgery, was 15-8 last year. He won the Cy Young 
Award with Kansas City in 1985 and '89. 
</P>
