<HEADLINE> Roll Call on Kosovo Spending Bill </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	The 311-105 roll call Thursday by which the House passed a bill  
providing $13.1 billion for the fighting with Yugoslavia and 
military improvements. 
</P>
<P>
	A ``yes'' vote is a vote to approve the bill.  
</P>
<P>
